Bugzilla is not for usage questions or help. Please use the mailing list or community sites like Stack Overflow for help. Kiwiwing's answer on SO should get you headed in the right direction.

If you discover a bug in POI, please file a bug with a minimum code sample to reproduce the problem, including any necessary files, setup instructions, and error messages. If you want to contribute an enhancement, open a bug with the patch and appropriate unit tests.
